descriptions.stg_users: Light cleaning of raw users. One row per user.
descriptions.stg_products: Light cleaning of raw products. One row per product.
descriptions.stg_orders: Light cleaning of raw orders. One row per order.
descriptions.stg_order_items: Light cleaning of raw order items. One row per line item.
descriptions.stg_events: Light cleaning of raw events. One row per event.
descriptions.dim_users: One row per user. Contains user attributes and account age.
descriptions.dim_products: One row per product. Contains product attributes and margin.
descriptions.fct_orders: One row per order line item. Contains order and product details with calculated margins.
descriptions.fct_events: One row per event. Contains event details and event sequence within user.
